<p><img src="https://www.bergtour-online.de/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Krottenkopf-Titel-1.jpg" alt="Krottenkopf" /></p>

<p><strong>Estergebierge</strong></p>

<hr />
<p>Ascent:  4:00 h
Descent:  3:00 h
Altitude difference: 1400 - 1500 m vert.
Season: End of June - Oktober.
Type: Long and difficult mountain hike.
—</p>

<p><strong>Charakter:</strong> high endurance neccessary due to 1500m vert.</p>

<p><strong>Drive to base:</strong>
1) At Loisachbrücke 5, 82496 Oberau. ,2) Farchat ,or 3) Eschenlohe.</p>

<p><strong>Approach:</strong>
It is possible to start from 1)Oberau, 2)Farchant, or 3) Eschenlohe.</p>

